Text: Sell WeekendThanks for the phone call a couple of weeks ago My wife and I will have a chance to see Houston this weekend as part of Enrons Sell Weekend A team of Enron employees including some Darden alums has planned many activities for us this weekend Its a great opportunity for her to know the city and I am sure well have a good time Hope everything is well Steve Pan Darden Business School Class of University Of Virginia Ivy Drive Charlottesville VA Tel
